{"tid":886070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[司法部出手] 美國控中台企業 偷取美光商業機密","createTime":"2018-11-02T00:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T08:52:43.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d931620937809bfcf9da6ca100caef67f403d796","tid":886070,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:04:40.000Z","msg":"美國控中台企業 偷取美光商業機密<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1982063\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1982063&d=J6RhEfzMus7NitM9hdRZVACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=58e06bb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1982063</a><br />\n<br />\n美國司法部起訴中台兩間公司與三名人士，涉及偷取美光科技的研發項目機密。<br />\n<br />\n被起訴分別是台灣Microelectronics Corp、中國福建晉華集成電路(Fujian Jinhua Integrated Circuit)，以及三名人士。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這是美國司法部自9月以來第四度指控中國間諜涉及偷取美國商業機密。</span><br />\n<br />\n司法部長塞申斯在記者會上指出，中國間諜活動增長迅速，因而美國政府將展開新行動，以打擊相關活動。除了刑事檢控外，司法部今次也作出民事訴，阻止中資公司出口與商業機密有關的產品。他表示，涉案的台灣公司與中國公司合作，以致中國間諜可偷取相關機密。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聯邦調查局局長克里斯托弗．雷(Christopher Wray)表示，沒有國家可對美國的創意與經濟安全構成威脅。</span>"},{"pid":"8586e1e79a324a9961a7c922c04320fe5dbfe9ce","tid":886070,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab002823038276713f1bcd37a084929240d1d68","tid":886070,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efae94759979b6b8986a5a4e285fd48d9b3195f3","tid":886070,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}